      "span_text": "Their patient cohort of 125 healthy male volunteers and 90 prostate cancer patients was subjected to pelvic MRI using 1.5 Tesla machine, pelvic phased array coil, and maximum value of 800 s/mm 2 . They found negative correlation between ADC value and Gleason score of cancer in peripheral zone proved on core biopsy specimen [CITATION_1] ."
